flowchart TD
  A[Start worker session\nkvdf multi-ai evolution session worker --watch] --> B[Load local project and Wi-Fi runtime state]
  B --> C[Advertise readiness on Wi-Fi/LAN]
  B --> D[Actively discover master on Wi-Fi/LAN]
  C --> E[Send bootstrap worker_join_request]
  D --> E
  E --> F{Master visible or join accepted?}
  F -- No --> G[Keep retrying in readiness mode]
  G --> C
  F -- Yes --> H[Wait for assignment packet]
  H --> I[Accept only approved scoped task]
  I --> J[Edit only leased files]
  J --> K[Run assigned tests]
  K --> L[Send heartbeat packets while working]
  L --> M[Send completion/result packet]
  M --> N[Wait for master acknowledgement]
